---
title: Turkey Meatball Parm Subs made with Pre-Cooked Turkey Meatballs
description: There are few sandwich combos more satisfying in this world than toasty bread, gooey cheese, and saucy meatballs. Here, we channel those winning flavors and textures into subs that are ready in just 10 minutes from start to finish—that’s faster than it takes to order out from your favorite sandwich shop! Our secret? The ultimate weeknight meatball hack: pre-cooked turkey meatballs, which we toss in an herby tomato sauce, then layer onto garlic-butter-toasted baguettes with melty mozz. It doesn’t get any better than that, folks.
